summary: Greatly expands Dushnik Yal, an Orc stronghold in the Reach.
descriptionHtml:
[left][size=6]A PLACE FIT FOR AN ORC
[/size]

This mod expands Dushnik Yal. 
It annexes Reachwind Eyrie, adds guards, adds a treasure house, (you can't really take anything, it's mostly for looks.) an archer nest in the tree, a huge statue to Malacath, a few new houses, and guard barracks. 

TO INSTALL:
Just put the .esp file in the Data folder.[/left]
author: Ronin
